{"tid":1866523,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[變態］［靈體］偽城","createTime":"2020-02-06T18:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T05:27:23.000Z","uid":189946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c89e2f0c0894998f8d0394802448e85802d3b7c0","tid":1866523,"uid":189946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:58:45.000Z","msg":"撈圳的大街上，顯得異常的寂靜。<br />\n<br />\n這一天，在被鄰近的香城共和國佔領後。一個名義上的部長，事實上香城共和國的總祭司帶同兩個女副手到達撈圳。<br />\n<br />\n這一天的旅途上，帶回來的。是一批從小就被寵壞的孩子。"},{"pid":"af1528a1e542569b1cca9db7cbd56e7db0538eff","tid":1866523,"uid":87189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T19:05:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兩盒，thanks🙏</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f61bacba7bb01ff0c63e94feee10971caf937123","tid":1866523,"uid":189946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"這一批兒童被帶到一間房子內，在房間內傳就兩種聲音，分別是鞭打及尖叫的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n一個一個的被閹割的閹童被送到學校內。"},{"pid":"7b371875b8eeadd1ec048c3a1325354a318b1cbe","tid":1866523,"uid":32612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T01:11:23.000Z","msg":"全故完？"},{"pid":"f687f761467aa1c2bd325f40e016afa678235b69","tid":1866523,"uid":189946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b371875b8eeadd1ec048c3a1325354a318b1cbe","tid":1866523,"uid":32612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T01:11:23.000Z","msg":"全故完？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T01:38:02.000Z","msg":"未，冇人睇咪唔寫"},{"pid":"b3d565c2fd3f41dda97c5c081cfa2e7068502c43","tid":1866523,"uid":32612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f687f761467aa1c2bd325f40e016afa678235b69","tid":1866523,"uid":189946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b371875b8eeadd1ec048c3a1325354a318b1cbe","tid":1866523,"uid":32612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T01:11:23.000Z","msg":"全故完？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T01:38:02.000Z","msg":"未，冇人睇